These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, taxi
1. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Game   | scrabble | chess | poker    |
| Transport     | subway    | taxi       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, train, boat
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Transport   | motorbike  | train  | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, august
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, r&b, techno
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday           | august | january | april |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | techno    | r&b        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, cape-coding, video-games
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cape-coding##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cape-coding##3
3. the cape-cod house is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | cape-coding | baking |
| House     | gothic-revival  | cape-cod    | colonial  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, metal, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of d&b is between the fan of metal and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | d&b | hip-hop |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

