.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, whist
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Game   | whist | poker | monopoly      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

