.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, rock, techno
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, woodworking, cooking
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | techno    | funk       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | cooking | chess |

