.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, rat
1. the person drinking cola is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Pet       | rat | guinea-pig | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, carrot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, techno
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Food           | nectarine | grapefruit | carrot |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco | r&b     |

