.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
House: colonial, townhouse, art-deco
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, musical, scientific
1. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
3. the colonial house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| House      | colonial | townhouse    | art-deco      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical       | animation | scientific |

