.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dunhill, pall-mall
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk         | fanta          |
| Cigar        | havana | dunhill | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, musician, project-manager
1. the coach is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the musician is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the coach is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| Job   | musician | coach | project-manager |

