.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, photography
3 different pets are kept: cat, horse, rabbit
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the cat##2
4. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | photography | fishing |
| Pet           | horse    | rabbit    | cat       |

