.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-17::.
City: hannover, edinburgh, paris
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| City       | paris    | edinburgh | hannover  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van        | scooter |

