.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, baseball, parkour
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | parkour    | baseball | skiing         |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts  | documentary |

 